response.overview: Wonderous Girl foils the plans of a local crime syndicate when she shows up during an arms sale. She makes quick work of the leader until he recovers and reveals his inhuman strength by giving Wonderous Girl a dose of her own medicine. Wonderous Girl keeps her cool as the battle ensues but her weaknesses are discovered after taking a low blow! The villain capitalizes on this and continues to target her most vulnerable and sensitive areas! Wonderous Girl manages to get the upper hand but only to realize she is now outnumbered! The leader reveals Wonderous Girl's secrets to his goons who waste no time and attack the young heroine where it counts the most. Wonderous Girl fights to the bitter end but each blow to her crotch and breasts weaken her giving advantage to her foes. Wonderous Girl takes endures a vicious beating and humiliating sexual advances to all parts of her luscious amazon body.
response.title: Vulnerability
